                            <comment id="24745" author="springboy" created="Tue, 10 Jul 2007 20:19:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi William&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I agree that &amp;lt;form:errors/&amp;gt; is a pretty coarse mechanism for displaying errors. The delimiter between individual errors can now be controlled (see the Javadoc), but it is nowhere near as flexible as you&apos;d like.&lt;/p&gt;

